author: bryanduxbury
msg: THRIFT-713. java: Java compareTo method throws NPE when any field isn't set.
This patch fixes a somewhat egregious bug in the generated compareTo for non-union structs and avoids possible NPEs.

author: mrglavas
msg: Adding an internal feature called: "http://apache.org/xml/features/internal/strings-interned". This makes it possible for applications to notify a ValidatorHandler that they are providing it with interned strings, allowing the ValidatorHandler to avoid passing strings for XML names through the SymbolTable.
